memberdef.name: URHO3D_AUTOMATIC_FLAGSET
memberdef.initializer: inline Urho3D::FlagSet<Enum> operator | (const Enum lhs, const Enum rhs) { return Urho3D::FlagSet<Enum>(lhs) | rhs; } \ inline Urho3D::FlagSet<Enum> operator & (const Enum lhs, const Enum rhs) { return Urho3D::FlagSet<Enum>(lhs) & rhs; } \ inline Urho3D::FlagSet<Enum> operator ^ (const Enum lhs, const Enum rhs) { return Urho3D::FlagSet<Enum>(lhs) ^ rhs; } \ inline Urho3D::FlagSet<Enum> operator ~ (const Enum rhs) { return ~Urho3D::FlagSet<Enum>(rhs); }

briefdescription.para: Make bitwise operators (| & ^ ~) automatically construct FlagSet from Enum.
Declare FlagSet for specific enum and create operators for automatic FlagSet construction.
